trans-unit.source: Provides the <xref uid="langword_csharp_abstract" name="abstract" href=""></xref> base class for a collection of associated <xref:System.String> keys and <xref:System.Object> values that can be accessed either with the key or with the index.
trans-unit.target: Gir den <xref uid="langword_csharp_abstract" name="abstract" href=""> </xref> basisklasse for en samling av tilknyttede <xref:System.String>nøkler og <xref:System.Object>verdier som kan åpnes med nøkkel eller med indeksen.</xref:System.Object> </xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: The underlying structure for this class is a hash table.
trans-unit.target: Den underliggende strukturen for denne klassen er en hash-tabell.

trans-unit.source: Each element is a key/value pair.
trans-unit.target: Hvert element er en nøkkel/verdi-paret.

trans-unit.source: The capacity of a NameObjectCollectionBase is the number of elements the NameObjectCollectionBase can hold.
trans-unit.target: Kapasiteten for en NameObjectCollectionBase er antallet elementer i NameObjectCollectionBase kan inneholde.

trans-unit.source: As elements are added to a NameObjectCollectionBase, the capacity is automatically increased as required through reallocation.
trans-unit.target: Som elementer er lagt til i en NameObjectCollectionBase, kapasiteten økes automatisk etter behov via ny tildeling.

trans-unit.source: The hash code provider dispenses hash codes for keys in the NameObjectCollectionBase instance.
trans-unit.target: Leverandør av hash-kode dispenses hash-koder for nøkler i NameObjectCollectionBase-forekomsten.

trans-unit.source: The default hash code provider is the <xref:System.Collections.CaseInsensitiveHashCodeProvider>.
trans-unit.target: Standardleverandøren for hash-koden er <xref:System.Collections.CaseInsensitiveHashCodeProvider>.</xref:System.Collections.CaseInsensitiveHashCodeProvider>

trans-unit.source: The comparer determines whether two keys are equal.
trans-unit.target: Sammenligningsfunksjonen bestemmer om to nøkler er like.

trans-unit.source: The default comparer is the <xref:System.Collections.CaseInsensitiveComparer>.
trans-unit.target: Standardsammenligningen er <xref:System.Collections.CaseInsensitiveComparer>.</xref:System.Collections.CaseInsensitiveComparer>

trans-unit.source: In .NET Framework version 1.0, this class uses culture-sensitive string comparisons.
trans-unit.target: I .NET Framework, versjon 1.0 bruker denne klassen kultur sensitive strengsammenligninger.

trans-unit.source: However, in .NET Framework version 1.1 and later, this class uses <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.InvariantCulture%2A?displayProperty=fullName> when comparing strings.
trans-unit.target: I .NET Framework, versjon 1.1 og nyere, bruker imidlertid denne klassen <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.InvariantCulture%2A?displayProperty=fullName>ved sammenligning av strenger.</xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.InvariantCulture%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: For more information about how culture affects comparisons and sorting, see [Performing Culture-Insensitive String Operations](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om hvordan kultur påvirker sammenligninger og sortering [utfører kultur bokstaver strengoperasjoner](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
